      <title>特使表示，菲律宾和美国打算在三月举行“2加2”会议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-intend-hold-2-plus-2-meeting-march-envoy-says-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾驻华盛顿大使周一表示，菲律宾和美国打算三月份在马尼拉举行高级外交和国防官员“2加2会议”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-intend-hold-2-plus-2-meeting-march-envoy-says-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:39:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的中国恒大重返法庭进行清算听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者和消费者信心低迷仍然是中国经济的主要拖累，开发商的清算裁决可能会震动脆弱的中国资本和房地产市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/embattled-china-evergrande-back-court-liquidation-hearing-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:15:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚 Woolworths 将对新西兰企业收取 10 亿澳元的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australias-woolworths-record-near-1-billion-impairment-2024-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Woolworths 周一表示，将在 2024 年中期业绩中记录 16 亿新西兰元（9.744 亿美元）的非现金减值，因为该连锁超市的新西兰业务在市场前景疲弱的情况下面临挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/australias-woolworths-record-near-1-billion-impairment-2024-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 22:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝中社称，朝鲜测试了潜射巡航导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-tests-submarine-launched-cruise-missile-kcna-says-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据官方媒体周一报道，朝鲜周日在一周内第二次测试了新型战略巡航导弹，称其为新开发的潜射巡航导弹（SLCM），加速了其海军核军备的发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-tests-submarine-launched-cruise-missile-kcna-says-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 21:28:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾前领导人之子称马科斯总统“懒惰”，敦促他辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-philippine-leaders-son-calls-president-marcos-lazy-urges-him-quit-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾前领导人罗德里戈·杜特尔特的儿子周日敦促总统小费迪南德·马科斯辞职，称他在两个政治强大家族之间日益加深的裂痕中懒惰且缺乏同情心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-philippine-leaders-son-calls-president-marcos-lazy-urges-him-quit-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 16:35:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不丹自由派托盖伊在第四次自由投票后成为总理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bhutans-liberal-tobgay-becomes-prime-minister-after-fourth-free-vote-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不丹自由派政治家、人民民主党（PDP）领导人策林·托盖（Tshering Tobgay）在本月早些时候的选举后于周日正式开始他的第二个总理任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bhutans-liberal-tobgay-becomes-prime-minister-after-fourth-free-vote-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 13:34:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国允许菲律宾向争议岛礁派遣部队</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海警表示，已做出“临时特别安排”，允许菲律宾通过一艘停泊在争议礁石上的二战时期船只向部队运送物资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 13:08:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教皇呼吁结束战争并敦促尊重平民</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pope-calls-an-end-wars-urges-respect-civilians-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[教皇方济各周日敦促尊重冲突地区的平民，并表示人们厌倦了战争，他称战争是“人民的灾难和人类的失败”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/pope-calls-an-end-wars-urges-respect-civilians-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 12:43:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚新南威尔士州总理谴责新纳粹集会</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-new-south-wales-state-premier-condemns-neo-nazi-rally-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚新南威尔士州州长周日谴责该州首府悉尼的新纳粹集会“令人震惊”，此前一天，总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯表示该国新纳粹主义正在抬头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-new-south-wales-state-premier-condemns-neo-nazi-rally-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 05:38:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国与泰国签署互免签证协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-sign-mutual-visa-waiver-agreements-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国和中国周日同意免除对方国民的签证要求，以促进受新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 影响的两国之间的旅行和旅游业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-sign-mutual-visa-waiver-agreements-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 05:26:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
